Qc7 { Protecting the b7-bishop from the threat of dxc5. } 8. Ne5
{ Temporarily sacrificing a pawn for the sake of initiative } 8... O-O 9. Bxb7
Qxb7 10. dxc5 Qe4
{ This is the key move, the last piece in the puzzle of securing equality for Black! You can check this line in more depth in the corresponding chapter. }
