{ Intending e3-e4, but why doesn't White play @@StartFEN@@rn1qkb1r/pb1p1p1p/1p3pp1/2p5/3P4/2P2N2/PP1NPPPP/R2QKB1R w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7.e4  in the first place? }
8... f5 { Creating a grip on the e4-square. } 9. O-O O-O 10. Qb3 Qc7
