{ An amazing tactical strike that gives Black the initiative! } 12. dxe5 dxe5
13. Nxe5
{ 13.Bxe5?!  for sure doesn't bring White anything after  13...Nxe5  14.Nxe5  Nd5  with more than enough compensation. }
13... Nh5 { Picking up the bishop pair. } 14. Nxd7 { The only move. } 14...
Nxf4 15. exf4 Qxd7 16. Nc4 { Protecting the b2-pawn but after } 16... Rfe8 17.
Ne3 Qd4 { Black has a menacing initiative. } *

