13... Nxe3 { This typical sacrifice is again very strong. } 14. fxe3 Rxe3+ 15.
Kf2
{ 15.Be2  is met with  15...Bxf3  16.Qxd8  Rxd8  17.gxf3  Rde8  -+  picking up material. }
