{ Making full use of the initiative. Black stands clearly better here. Let's see what will happen if White tries to hold on to the a2 pawn. }
20. a3 Na2+ { Self-trap our knight to lure White's king out. } 21. Kc2
{ 21.Kb1?  Rd1+  22.Kxa2  Rxf1!-+  is the point. } 21... Bf5+ 22. Kb3 Nc1+ 23.
Kc3 Rd1 { Black is winning due to the pin on the 1st rank. } *

