{ Shoring up the e5-pawn. } 16. Nd3 Nh5
{ Both sides have their chances in this complicated position. White will be preparing f4, but it's not possible right now as g3 would be hanging. Meanwhile, we will strive to carry out the f5 break at the best moment. }
