{ 15.Rb1?  looks natural, intending Na4. However, Black wins with  15...Ng4!  16.Na4  Nxe3!  17.Nxb6  Nxd1-+  and Black is just winning. White's idea is to play Nc4 and win the c5-knight, but we can cut across this plan. }
