{ 10.Nbd2  Bc3!  and  10.Nfd2  Bd4!  are both very annoying for White. } 10...
Qxd2+ 11. Nbxd2 Bc3 12. Bxb5 Bxd5
{ Black is out of any danger and is slightly better here. } *

