{ Opening the way for the rook. Next, Black will play Rb8 next with sufficient compensation for the pawn.   That's the end of the theory section of this course. Hope you will score many points, boost your chess understanding and have some original moments with an original opening: the Spielmann-Indian. If you have any questions, feel free to post a comment in that position. I promise I will answer your questions as soon as possible. Good luck! }
